  "product": {
    "id": 10065448698172,
    "title": "SeaKing E09 White Fiberglass Fillet Table (L32.3\" x W18.1\")",
    "body_html": "<p> </p>\n<div data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"ProductItem-details-excerpt\" data-content-field=\"excerpt\">\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\"> <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<span>The SeaKing SK-E09 stands out as a premium option in the SeaKing Range, characterised by its </span><span>ergonomic design. It includes a spacious knife tray positioned at the front for quick and easy access, </span><span>along with a deep storage sink featuring a drain. A distinctive feature of this board is its raised lip </span><span>around the sides and back, ensuring secure retention of items even in rough conditions. </span>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Handcrafted </span><span>using top-grade composite materials, it incorporates a UV resistant PE plastic cutting board for </span><span>durability. Crafted to meet the demands of serious anglers, this board combines functionality with </span><span>premium quality materials, making it an excellent choice for fishing enthusiasts seeking reliability and </span><span>performance on the water.</span></p>\n<b id=\"docs-internal-guid-eff1bc17-7fff-9f22-7b22-7543c63b32ac\"></b>\n</div>",
